{"lemma":"نِرْجِسُ","slug":"نِرْجِسُ","root":"ن.ر.ج.س","root_slug":"ن-ر-ج-س","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ر-ج-س","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["name","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n39640","n14877"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%90%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%AC%D9%90%D8%B3%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"Narcissus gen. et spp."},{"pos":"name","gloss":"a female given name"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Middle Persian [Book Pahlavi needed] (nlgs /⁠nargis⁠/), from Ancient Greek νάρκισσος (nárkissos)."},"ipa":["/nar.d͡ʒis/","[ˈnærɡes]"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n39640","headword_ar":"نَرْجِسٌ","root":"nrjs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nirojisN","text_ar":"نِرْجِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The Narcissus"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rjs","text_ar":"رجس"},{"kind":"text","text":". The former is mentioned by ISd in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rjs","text_ar":"رجس"},{"kind":"text","text":": the latter, in the present art. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n14877","headword_ar":"نَرْجِسٌ","root":"rjs","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nirojisN","text_ar":"نِرْجِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, Sgh, Msb, K) [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"narcissus;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain sweet-smelling flower,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"well known:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the smell of which is beneficial for the cold rheum and the cold headache:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) the word is arabicized, (S, Msb, TA,) from [the Persian]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naroGiso","text_ar":"نَرْگِسْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) [this being the case, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"n","text_ar":"ن"},{"kind":"text","text":"should be regarded as radical it is said, however, that] the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"n","text_ar":"ن"},{"kind":"text","text":"in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"narojisN","text_ar":"نَرْجِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is augmentative, because there is no word of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEolilN","text_ar":"فَعْلِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but there is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafoEilN","text_ar":"نَفْعِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) though only what is changed, in application, from a verb: (Msb:) but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nirojisN","text_ar":"نِرْجِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEolilu","text_ar":"فِعْلِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) or it is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nifoEilN","text_ar":"نِفْعِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the augmentative letter being made to accord in its vowel with the radical letter in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*oxirN","text_ar":"اـِذْخِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and that in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ivomidN","text_ar":"اـِثْمِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.: (Msb:) or, accord. to IDrd,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"narojisN","text_ar":"نَرْجِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEolilN","text_ar":"فَعْلِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and the only instance of that measure. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nrjs","text_ar":"نرجس"},{"kind":"text","text":".) If you name a man"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"narojis","text_ar":"نَرْجِس"},{"kind":"text","text":", you make it imperfectly decl., because it is like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naDoribu","text_ar":"نَضْرِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) but if you name him"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nirojis","text_ar":"نِرْجِس"},{"kind":"text","text":", it is perfectly decl., because it is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEolilN","text_ar":"فِعْلِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) [or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nifoEilN","text_ar":"نِفْعِلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", neither of which is the measure of a verb]. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"narojisu AlmaAy^idapi","text_ar":"نَرْجِسُ المَايِدَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zumaAwarodN","text_ar":"زُمَاوَرْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","AA","Sgh","TA"]}]}}